1
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:40,360
May I be like the stars

2
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,580
and you like the moon.

3
00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:43,670
As long as the world remains,

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,780
so shall we.

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

6
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,370
I want to be with you forever.

8
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

9
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,480
You and she are ultimately different.

10
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,600
Have you ever

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,789
truly cared for me?

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,250
No.

13
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,360
Never.

14
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:57,720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

15
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,310
May we live and die together,

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,040
and share life and death as one.

17
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:45,710
[Moonlight Mystique]

18
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:49,990
[Episode 6]

19
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,470
Without me,

20
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,360
the Contemplation Stone

21
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,000
is useless to you.

22
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,750
Since it's in my body,

23
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:03,280
I have the final say

24
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,960
who it belongs to.

25
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:06,960
Your acting is pretty good.

26
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:12,830
Bai Shuo.

27
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,530
You know clearly that

28
00:03:15,260 --> 00:03:17,050
I need you to gather the Contemplations

29
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:18,870
and activate the Contemplation Stone.

30
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:21,290
Not only will I not kill you, but I'll also protect you.

31
00:03:21,290 --> 00:03:22,520
However, the Eternals

32
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,810
will only try to kill you to retrieve the Contemplation Stone

33
00:03:24,810 --> 00:03:27,200
or lock you up with the Contemplation Stone

34
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:29,670
for the so-called "bigger picture."

35
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:31,930
So it might seem that I took you away with me,

36
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:34,280
but in fact, you voluntarily followed me.

37
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:35,690
Am I right?

38
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,540
Bai Xun was killed by the Demon Race.

39
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:39,970
I know you want to become stronger

40
00:03:39,970 --> 00:03:41,250
and seek revenge,

41
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:42,700
but you can't count on the Human Race.

42
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:45,220
You can only choose between the Eternal Race and the Demon Race.

43
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:47,340
You've seen the incompetence of the Eternal Race.

44
00:03:47,340 --> 00:03:49,670
The Eternal Race is not your first choice.

45
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,280
You know very well that

46
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,730
only the Bright Moon Palace

47
00:03:52,730 --> 00:03:54,860
can truly help you.

48
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,800
But you wouldn't admit defeat to me.

49
00:03:57,850 --> 00:03:59,610
Now that I brought you back,

50
00:03:59,730 --> 00:04:02,010
I've given you an excuse to save face,

51
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,740
right?

52
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,960
Don't be so conceited.

53
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,360
Without the Bright Moon Palace,

54
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,910
I can still kill Zhen Yu and Fu Ling.

55
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:13,550
Good.

56
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:16,640
I like the way you act tough.

57
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:22,280
Don't you want to seek revenge on your own?

58
00:04:22,290 --> 00:04:23,510
Come on.

59
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:25,350
I'll stand right here

60
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:27,080
and won't move a step.

61
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:29,720
If you could do me even the slightest harm,

62
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,630
I'll let you go immediately,

63
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:34,720
and I won't ask about the Contemplation Stone anymore.

64
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,200
You said it yourself.

65
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,360
Again.

66
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:08,390
Do you think us Three Kings of the Demon Race

67
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,850
got our title for nothing?

68
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:12,040
Zhen Yu is no weaker than me.

69
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,630
You can't even get close to me,

70
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,040
yet you dream about killing him?

71
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,660
Your mediocre skills

72
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:19,390
may be more than enough to fight among the Human Race,

73
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:21,480
but in the face of absolute power,

74
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:22,780
you are nothing.

75
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:26,100
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

76
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:30,010
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

77
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:32,830
♫This moment feels like forever♫

78
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,360
Your resistance now

79
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:36,050
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

80
00:05:33,380 --> 00:05:35,380
is just an outlet for your emotions.

81
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:40,070
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

82
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,409
You don't have any choice anymore.

83
00:05:38,409 --> 00:05:39,400
Bai Shuo.

84
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:42,190
♫Even if I'll perish♫

85
00:05:42,580 --> 00:05:45,220
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

86
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:48,250
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

87
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:57,060
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

88
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:53,950
You're considered smart

89
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,310
among humans.

90
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,390
Although you wouldn't admit

91
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:58,200
what I said just now is true,

92
00:05:58,250 --> 00:05:59,810
you know very well that

93
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:02,280
only when you become strong enough to intimidate your opponent

94
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,980
can your revenge begin.

95
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,200
What if I want to kill you too?

96
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,440
As long as you can.

97
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,920
You've got something to say?

98
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,510
Why did you do that, Master?

99
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:30,820
I just don't want her to run around with the Contemplation Stone.

100
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:32,110
If it's just to control her,

101
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:33,580
there are many ways.

102
00:06:33,610 --> 00:06:36,070
Why did you choose the most troublesome one?

103
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,360
What are you trying to say?

104
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,780
I just want to remind you, Master,

105
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:41,480
not to be swayed by some momentary compassion.

106
00:06:41,610 --> 00:06:44,040
There are only three stars left on the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

107
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,810
If the stars are all gone, even if Bai Shuo doesn't kill you,

108
00:06:46,810 --> 00:06:48,950
there will be no Master of the Bright Moon Palace in the world anymore.

109
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:50,630
I know what I'm doing.

110
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,620
She's a human who broke into the fight between Eternals and demons.

111
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:55,870
She must learn the abilities to protect herself.

112
00:06:55,870 --> 00:06:58,070
Otherwise, how can she be my ally?

113
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:06,650
Bai Shuo can activate the Contemplation Stone?

114
00:07:06,650 --> 00:07:07,770
Sect Leader.

115
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:08,870
Please allow me

116
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,750
to lead troops to the Polar Region to bring Bai Shuo back.

117
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:13,190
Of course we must retrieve the Contemplation Stone.

118
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:16,720
It's just the Polar Region stretches for hundreds of thousands of miles.

119
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:20,350
To this day, no one knows where the Bright Moon Palace is.

120
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,510
We can only send disciples

121
00:07:22,530 --> 00:07:24,880
to locate the Bright Moon Palace first.

122
00:07:25,370 --> 00:07:26,690
Once they find it,

123
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:29,160
they'll bring Bai Shuo back.

124
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:31,830
I thought you

125
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:34,120
went to negotiate with Fan Yue, Sect Leader.

126
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,390
When you came back, you even said Fan Yue was nice,

127
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:38,790
and that he would let Bai Shuo make her own choice.

128
00:07:38,790 --> 00:07:39,620
But look what happened. Where is she?

129
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:42,550
Who can help me out here?

130
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:46,320
The Demon Race is fickle

131
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,300
and has no moral principles.

132
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:50,430
This is not something Sect Leader could have predicted.

133
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,330
Sect Leader.

134
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,430
Where is Chong Zhao?

135
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,920
Why haven't I seen him since he came back?

136
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,310
He knew he was at fault,

137
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:58,050
and he petitioned for a self-imposed punishment of 300 Red Bone Whips.

138
00:07:58,050 --> 00:07:59,570
300 Red Bone Whips?

139
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:06,630
The Red Bone Whip is Lanling's punishment for felonies.

140
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:08,030
Every whip will hurt the bone.

141
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:09,610
It may seem to cause physical injuries,

142
00:08:09,610 --> 00:08:11,540
but it actually tortures the soul.

143
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:26,460
Since you can't bear to see him like that, Sect Leader,

144
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:28,200
why did you agree to his petition

145
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,580
and let him be punished so heavily?

146
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,730
He should be punished for his mistake.

147
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:34,220
He cannot be let off the hook for the chaos he brought to Ning'an.

148
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:36,030
Besides the 300 Red Bone Whips,

149
00:08:36,049 --> 00:08:38,789
he also needs to reflect on his mistakes at the Heart-guarding Cliff.

150
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:40,320
That being said,

151
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,890
the real sinner is the Cold Spring Palace.

152
00:08:42,970 --> 00:08:45,840
The Cold Spring Palace violated the iron law between Eternals and demons

153
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:49,100
and harmed the Human Race. Of course it should be executed.

154
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:50,470
Yan Huo.

155
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,430
Send a letter to the 72 Sects

156
00:08:53,450 --> 00:08:55,340
and invite all Sect Leaders here

157
00:08:55,370 --> 00:08:57,670
to discuss the crusade against the Cold Spring Palace.

158
00:08:57,670 --> 00:08:58,620
Yes.

159
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:00,410
Go.

160
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:04,850
Now,

161
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:07,410
the Contemplation Stone has been brought to the Bright Moon Palace by Fan Yue.

162
00:09:07,410 --> 00:09:09,320
It won't be easy if we want to take it by force.

163
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:12,310
Then it depends on whether my beloved disciple, Fu Ling,

164
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:15,230
can make Chong Zhao defect or not.

165
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,740
Grand Master, so you want to take advantage of Chong Zhao's relationship

166
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:19,170
with Bai Shuo?

167
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,160
Before he dies,

168
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:23,220
if

169
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:24,850
he can really

170
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:27,800
lure out Bai Shuo and the Contemplation Stone for me,

171
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:29,370
that will be

172
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:31,240
his last glory.

173
00:09:41,260 --> 00:09:42,530
I'll choose

174
00:09:42,610 --> 00:09:44,010
my own path.

175
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:46,500
No one has the right to make decisions for me.

176
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:53,990
Master.

177
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,390
Master.

178
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,680
Maybe you should go check on Bai Shuo.

179
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:04,360
She hasn't eaten or drunk anything for two days.

180
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:06,220
She may die anytime.

181
00:10:06,370 --> 00:10:08,040
She knows what she wants.

182
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,390
She won't let herself die.

183
00:10:10,410 --> 00:10:11,940
Then why is she so stubborn?

184
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,340
It takes time to give in

185
00:10:16,430 --> 00:10:17,910
to someone you hate.

186
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,320
I'm in no rush.

187
00:10:32,690 --> 00:10:34,690
Here's the best medicine

188
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,720
and the sharpest knife in the Bright Moon Palace.

189
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,050
Whether you live or die,

190
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,600
it's your own choice.

191
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:47,060
The Bright Moon Palace never feeds half-dead losers.

192
00:10:55,450 --> 00:10:56,560
You choose to die?

193
00:10:57,170 --> 00:10:58,320
I can help you.

194
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:01,410
I'm the only one who can activate the Contemplation Stone.

195
00:11:01,410 --> 00:11:02,710
You dare not kill me,

196
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:04,300
nor can you.

197
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,510
What?

198
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,200
Are you really going to

199
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,590
rely on a lifeless thing for the rest of your life?

200
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:11,790
I thought you were a woman of character.

201
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:16,490
If I were you, I would choose the medicine.

202
00:11:16,490 --> 00:11:19,170
After all, your pride is worthless now.

203
00:11:19,450 --> 00:11:21,120
If you can really hide in silence in front of your enemies

204
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:23,630
and kill them with one strike,

205
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:26,000
I might think better of you.

206
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:42,460
I'll return it to you.

207
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,790
I'll wait.

208
00:11:57,610 --> 00:11:59,550
Weren't you worried that she might choose the knife?

209
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:01,210
She's not as weak as you think.

210
00:12:01,730 --> 00:12:03,160
Although she's a human,

211
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:05,610
the fact that she dared to step into the Bright Moon Palace

212
00:12:05,610 --> 00:12:07,360
shows that she's braver than

213
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,790
most people in the world.

214
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:10,960
Why do I sense some

215
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,280
admiration in your words?

216
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:23,300
[Heart-guarding Cliff
Lanling Sect, Eternal Race]

217
00:12:29,090 --> 00:12:30,720
You want to detoxify,

218
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:33,070
yet you refuse to report it to Lanling Sect.

219
00:12:33,070 --> 00:12:34,340
Why is that?

220
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:36,840
Because you're scared.

221
00:12:37,450 --> 00:12:39,530
The human with the Contemplation Stone in her body

222
00:12:39,530 --> 00:12:41,050
should be killed!

223
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,430
If you're not capable enough, even if you use your sword,

224
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:45,360
you'll only embarrass yourself.

225
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:46,670
Logically,

226
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,250
I have no right to blame you.

227
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,610
But emotionally,

228
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:51,510
I cannot help but blame you.

229
00:12:52,250 --> 00:12:53,920
From now on,

230
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,880
we go

231
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,500
our separate ways.

232
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:05,310
Being distracted when practicing martial skills.

233
00:13:05,310 --> 00:13:07,160
Do you want to die, Divinity?

234
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:11,480
It's you.

235
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:13,020
I'll kill you!

236
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:18,260
In Ning'an City,

237
00:13:18,290 --> 00:13:20,190
I saved you twice.

238
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,520
Instead of thanking me,

239
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,690
you want to kill me?

240
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:27,610
I should have killed you in the clinic.

241
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,980
Exactly. So

242
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:30,700
why did you save me that night?

243
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:33,200
You probably don't know that

244
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,060
I killed the doctor in the clinic.

245
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:36,720
I had no choice. He peeked at my body

246
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,000
without permission.

247
00:13:38,020 --> 00:13:38,900
Tell me.

248
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:40,490
Who do you think caused his death?

249
00:13:40,490 --> 00:13:42,210
You witch.

250
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:44,030
You gave up a city for one person.

251
00:13:44,060 --> 00:13:45,020
Chong Zhao.

252
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,970
How are you different from demons?

253
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,720
The Eternal Race is truly cruel.

254
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:51,290
You just made a tiny mistake,

255
00:13:51,290 --> 00:13:54,190
yet they erased your past achievements and exiled you here.

256
00:13:54,190 --> 00:13:56,520
The Heart-guarding Cliff is at the border of Lanling.

257
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:57,920
If you take another step,

258
00:13:57,950 --> 00:13:59,990
you'll be out of the territory of the Eternal Race.

259
00:13:59,990 --> 00:14:01,230
Chong Zhao.

260
00:14:01,260 --> 00:14:02,670
Why don't you leave Lanling

261
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,270
and join my Cold Spring Palace?

262
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:05,360
Dream on!

263
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:07,270
During Ning'an Xunyuan Lantern Festival,

264
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:09,570
inexorable doom befell the Lanling Eternal Envoys.

265
00:14:09,570 --> 00:14:11,640
They never came back.

266
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:14,000
Who is waiting for their return?

267
00:14:16,610 --> 00:14:18,410
How do you know these?

268
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,610
I was bored

269
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:22,200
and inquired about you.

270
00:14:22,230 --> 00:14:24,350
I found something strange.

271
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:26,360
Ten years ago, during the Xunyuan Lantern Festival,

272
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:28,740
the Human Race was attacked by the Demon Race, and hundreds of humans got killed or injured.

273
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:30,360
The Eternal Envoy of Lanling, Chong Tai,

274
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:32,230
