suspected the cause of death of his parents,

278
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,090
yet he found nothing after years of investigation.

279
00:14:39,090 --> 00:14:40,640
What are you trying to say?

280
00:14:40,660 --> 00:14:42,140
The entire Eternal Race knows that your parents

281
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:44,280
were killed by a scorpion demon ten years ago.

282
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,470
But do you know that

283
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:47,340
two days before your parents were killed,

284
00:14:47,340 --> 00:14:49,410
Qian Yin already died?

285
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,590
You've been investigating for so many years, but you found nothing.

286
00:14:52,590 --> 00:14:53,790
Do you know why?

287
00:14:54,450 --> 00:14:55,450
Because

288
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:59,740
you've never stepped on the territory of the Demon Race.

289
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:00,620
Chong Zhao.

290
00:15:00,650 --> 00:15:02,290
What you see now

291
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:03,950
may not be the truth.

292
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:05,920
But somewhere you can't see,

293
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,150
the truth

294
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:08,910
might be right there.

295
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,250
What do you mean?

296
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:16,420
I'll wait for you in the Cold Spring Palace

297
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:18,630
for a talk, Divinity Chong Zhao.

298
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:21,730
Master.

299
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:24,350
My parents were the best Eternal Envoys of Lanling.

300
00:15:24,350 --> 00:15:25,420
They killed countless demons.

301
00:15:25,420 --> 00:15:26,560
How could they have been

302
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,470
killed by a scorpion demon?

303
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:29,630
That's impossible!

304
00:15:29,630 --> 00:15:30,870
Kid.

305
00:15:30,890 --> 00:15:33,280
Didn't you see it with your own eyes?

306
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:36,210
Your parents' soul lamps have gone out.

307
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:38,170
It's all my fault.

308
00:15:38,310 --> 00:15:40,730
I underestimated the demonic power of Qian Yin

309
00:15:40,730 --> 00:15:42,760
and sent your parents to hunt him down,

310
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:45,530
which ended up getting them killed.

311
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:46,470
No!

312
00:15:46,490 --> 00:15:47,890
My father said

313
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,280
that even if they encountered any danger,

314
00:15:48,340 --> 00:15:51,860
♫That year, that year♫

315
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:52,060
one of them would come back alive.

316
00:15:52,090 --> 00:15:53,540
They wouldn't leave me behind.

317
00:15:52,490 --> 00:15:55,590
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

318
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:54,870
They said that.

319
00:15:56,380 --> 00:15:59,840
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

320
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:00,460
Don't worry.

321
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:03,230
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

322
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:03,440
I will kill Qian Yin myself

323
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,150
and avenge your parents.

324
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:07,310
♫That year, that year♫

325
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:06,790
Cultivate well

326
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,360
and live well.

327
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:10,900
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

328
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:11,600
That'll be the best solace

329
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:14,600
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

330
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,460
to your parents' souls in heaven.

331
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:18,570
♫Layer after layer♫

332
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:22,180
♫Another year passed♫

333
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:30,110
♫Another year passed♫

334
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,700
I thought you were dead.

335
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,280
Sorry to disappoint you.

336
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:39,870
I would only be disappointed if you really died.

337
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:41,600
Whether I have the Contemplation Stone or not,

338
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,150
I won't let myself die.

339
00:16:43,810 --> 00:16:44,990
Tell me then.

340
00:16:45,110 --> 00:16:46,310
What do you plan to do?

341
