346
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:58,320
I may see the second image of foresight

347
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,650
at any time.

348
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:01,980
If you want to know where the next Contemplation will be born,

349
00:17:01,980 --> 00:17:03,240
