356
00:17:17,220 --> 00:17:20,079
Only with bargaining chips can you do what you want.

357
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:22,740
You have a clear mind

358
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:24,319
and the right strategy.

359
00:17:24,339 --> 00:17:25,680
However,

360
00:17:25,730 --> 00:17:28,380
since you can make a deal out of the gathering of Contemplations,

361
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:30,510
why don't you just ask me to avenge you?

362
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:32,870
I must seek revenge in this world

363
00:17:32,870 --> 00:17:34,550
on my own.

364
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:37,710
My father's suffering,

365
00:17:37,850 --> 00:17:39,000
the blood he shed,

366
00:17:39,430 --> 00:17:40,600
and the life he lost.

367
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:41,880
One day,

368
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:44,610
I will take it all back from them with my own hands.

369
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,370
So, Master,

370
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,580
will you teach me

371
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,670
or not?

372
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:56,030
Most of these weapons were

373
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:57,740
left behind by the demons that were killed.

374
00:17:57,740 --> 00:18:00,340
So each weapon carries certain demonic power.

375
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:02,370
Which weapon is the strongest?

376
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,820
Greed won't do you any good.

377
00:18:05,850 --> 00:18:07,110
Since I want to practice,

378
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:09,640
