384
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,830
They might even get hurt by the fire patterns

385
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,490
and the demonic power within.

386
00:18:24,010 --> 00:18:26,170
Are you sure you want to practice with it?

387
00:18:26,170 --> 00:18:26,970
Yes.

388
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:56,690
She actually lifted it up.

389
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:59,850
Could it be that the Contemplation Stone is helping her?

390
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,590
I suggest you put it down now.

391
00:19:03,610 --> 00:19:04,820
I've said,

392
00:19:04,850 --> 00:19:07,620
I'll only practice with the most powerful weapon.

393
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:09,400
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

394
00:19:09,650 --> 00:19:11,700
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

395
00:19:11,930 --> 00:19:13,150
If you don't put it down now,

396
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:13,540
♫My love brought tears♫

397
00:19:13,180 --> 00:19:14,620
