00:19:51,940 --> 00:19:53,260
I said,

415
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:54,150
go back.

416
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:56,660
I never said I couldn't do it.

417
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:58,200
Are you moved by yourself?

418
00:19:58,780 --> 00:20:00,020
In my eyes,

419
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:01,420
you're just foolish.

420
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:03,630
I just don't want to give up.

421
00:20:04,130 --> 00:20:05,470
My injuries will heal,

422
00:20:05,630 --> 00:20:07,230
but the training can't stop.

423
00:20:07,850 --> 00:20:09,070
It takes a lot more than bravery

424
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:10,470
to achieve great things.

425
00:20:10,670 --> 00:20:12,060
If you get your hands crippled,

426
00:20:12,060 --> 00:20:13,620
I won't teach you anymore.

427
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,080
Tian Huo.

428
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,630
Escort her back.

429
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:29,130
You're cold and distant,

430
00:20:29,150 --> 00:20:31,280
and your dressing skills are average.

431
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:33,590
I don't think we are close enough

432
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:35,660
to talk about this.

433
00:20:36,210 --> 00:20:37,610
Let me remind you again.

434
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:40,650
Outside the Bright Moon Palace is the Polar Region that stretches for hundreds of thousands of miles.

435
00:20:40,650 --> 00:20:41,850
There are demons and monsters everywhere.

436
00:20:41,850 --> 00:20:43,400
Don't wander around.

437
00:20:43,430 --> 00:20:45,400
I won't be responsible if you lose your life.

438
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,930
I don't need your reminder.

439
00:20:47,230 --> 00:20:49,830
I have more important things to do with my life.

440
00:20:49,840 --> 00:20:51,160
That would be the best.

441
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:53,350
Don't make Master worry about you.

442
00:20:53,560 --> 00:20:55,090
You care about Fan Yue a lot?

443
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:58,270
Everyone in the Bright Moon Palace

444
00:20:58,270 --> 00:20:59,980
