445
00:21:00,070 --> 00:21:01,670
So just stay here and be good.

446
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:03,900
Master will teach you when he wants to.

447
00:21:04,010 --> 00:21:06,640
Don't have any ulterior motives.

448
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:09,080
Ulterior motives?

449
00:21:10,180 --> 00:21:12,030
