465
00:21:53,670 --> 00:21:59,350
♫All the answers are already explained♫

466
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:03,780
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

467
00:22:03,060 --> 00:22:03,970
Shuo.

468
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:07,610
♫But we're destined to part♫

469
00:22:05,580 --> 00:22:07,780
You may not succeed if you don't give up.

470
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:10,050
But if you give up, you'll definitely fail.

471
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:14,450
♫How can I downplay this?♫

472
00:22:11,710 --> 00:22:12,750
I believe in you.

473
00:22:15,060 --> 00:22:18,290
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

474
00:22:18,980 --> 00:22:21,860
♫When my star falls only for you♫

475
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:21,390
Father.

476
00:22:21,910 --> 00:22:23,180
Sorry.

477
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:24,060
♫When the heavens fall♫

478
00:22:23,830 --> 00:22:25,620
