482
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:32,980
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

483
00:22:31,090 --> 00:22:33,440
I will step on it,

484
00:22:33,460 --> 00:22:34,950
take the revenge

485
00:22:33,570 --> 00:22:37,630
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

486
00:22:34,970 --> 00:22:36,640
and repay the kindness that is due

487
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,110
step by step.

488
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:42,650
♫As you turn into a falling star♫

489
00:22:38,930 --> 00:22:39,960
Don't worry.

490
00:22:40,450 --> 00:22:42,880
I will forge my own path.

491
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:53,940
Get out of my way.

492
00:22:54,210 --> 00:22:55,280
Where is Fan Yue?

493
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:56,680
Do you think Master's whereabouts

494
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:58,020
