498
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:03,260
Since Master said he would teach you,

499
00:23:03,260 --> 00:23:04,540
of course he won't break his promise.

500
00:23:04,540 --> 00:23:05,820
But he also said

501
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:07,330
if your hands were crippled,

502
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,680
he wouldn't teach you anymore.

503
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,120
