00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:00,840
That's not wrong.

819
00:37:03,580 --> 00:37:04,840
Why aren't we going in?

820
00:37:05,030 --> 00:37:06,160
He already ran away.

821
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,030
Where are we going?

822
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:10,290
To catch the tortoise.

823
00:37:14,870 --> 00:37:16,990
Put me down!

824
00:37:22,510 --> 00:37:24,110
Stop it!

825
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:26,710
If you keep pulling the thread, my shell will crack.

826
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:28,650
Is this the Eternal you talked about?

827
00:37:28,650 --> 00:37:29,770
A real tor...

828
00:37:31,050 --> 00:37:32,200
Turtle.

829
00:37:32,470 --> 00:37:34,010
He's the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle.

830
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:35,000
He's lived longer

831
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,930
than the Five Eternals of Lanling.

832
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:41,890
Given his species, he can't die young even if he wants to.

833
00:37:51,950 --> 00:37:53,140
My old...

834
00:37:57,190 --> 00:37:59,280
I once saved your life in the Eternal Race.

835
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:00,200
Now,

836
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,820
I'm here to collect the debt.

837
00:38:09,780 --> 00:38:10,700
Fan Yue.

838
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:15,140
Why did you come to the Eternal Race's territory

839
00:38:15,140 --> 00:38:17,340
instead of staying in the Polar Region?

840
00:38:19,510 --> 00:38:21,280
Demon King of the Polar Region.

841
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:23,320
Master of Bright Moon.

842
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:25,400
Here comes another demon king.

843
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:28,490
Zhen Yu.

844
00:38:28,700 --> 00:38:30,960
I feel like you're actually regressing.

845
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,910
As the Demon King,

846
00:38:32,930 --> 00:38:34,440
you actually chased after a turtle?

847
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:36,640
I'm the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle.

848
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,420
The one in Lanling?

849
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:42,670
He knows me!

850
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:44,070
He...

851
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:46,520
I can do whatever I want.

852
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,400
What?

853
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:48,460
Today,

854
00:38:48,490 --> 00:38:49,820
you want to get involved

855
00:38:50,010 --> 00:38:51,470
and help the Eternal Race?

856
00:38:52,560 --> 00:38:53,760
So what if I help them?

857
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:56,120
The Jingyou Mountain has been silent for years.

858
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:58,550
Word has it in the Demon Race that the Three Kings have been fighting.

859
00:38:58,550 --> 00:38:59,510
But it seems to me that

860
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:01,510
it's just a fight between you and me.

861
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,250
I will save

862
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,680
whoever you want to kill.

863
00:39:04,730 --> 00:39:06,220
And I'll oppose

864
00:39:06,290 --> 00:39:07,620
whatever you want to do.

865
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,230
Haughty.

866
00:39:12,170 --> 00:39:13,170
Good.

867
00:39:13,210 --> 00:39:14,850
Let me see

868
00:39:15,410 --> 00:39:17,480
whether you, the new king of the Demon Race,

869
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,060
deserve

870
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:21,000
your arrogance.

871
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,440
Zhen Yu.

872
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:45,880
You are too old.

873
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:47,580
If you ask me,

874
00:39:48,170 --> 00:39:49,580
there doesn't have to be Three Kings

875
00:39:49,580 --> 00:39:50,850
in the Demon Race.

876
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:54,590
Fan Yue, don't get cocky too soon.

877
00:39:54,620 --> 00:39:55,980
One day,

878
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:59,030
I'll avenge the loss of my tail.

879
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:05,800
The teleportation formation I gave you back then

880
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:08,840
was for you to come to Lanling to see me anytime.

881
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,070
But look at you.

882
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:12,070
You haven't come to see me even once over these years.

883
00:40:12,070 --> 00:40:14,880
You even stole the Contemplation Stone with the treasure I gave you.

884
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:18,340
Public morals are indeed degenerating with each passing day.

885
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:19,840
Demons are heartless.

886
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,370
Why do I remember

887
00:40:21,390 --> 00:40:23,740
we made the plan to steal the Contemplation Stone together?

888
00:40:23,740 --> 00:40:25,260
Don't talk nonsense!

889
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,620
It has nothing to do with me.

890
00:40:26,620 --> 00:40:28,230
You stole it yourself.

891
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,960
But Jin Yao must be very curious

892
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:32,280
how I broke through all the barriers of the Eternals

893
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:34,510
and walked so freely in Lanling, don't you think?

894
00:40:34,510 --> 00:40:36,840
What exactly do you want?

895
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,090
Use your elixir

896
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:39,310
to cure her backlash.

897
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:40,890
What backlash?

898
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:46,150
The backlash caused by the conflict between the Contemplation Stone and the demonic power.

899
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:46,710
You...

900
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:49,550
So you're the human who absorbed the Contemplation Stone?

901
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:50,440
You...

902
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:52,240
Are you going to treat her or not?

903
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,590
Sure. Sure I will.

904
00:40:54,590 --> 00:40:55,230
Also,

905
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,970
teach her the Eternals' sorcery.

906
00:41:00,980 --> 00:41:02,870
You may as well tell Jin Yao

907
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:04,780
that I let you in.

908
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:06,750
I'll only lose a layer of my shell for colluding with the enemy.

909
00:41:06,750 --> 00:41:09,480
But if I teach her, I'm afraid I won't live to be a 1000-year-old tortoise.

910
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:10,630
I wouldn't dare to offend those five Eternals

911
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:12,450
at the same time.

912
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:14,190
Aren't you the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle

913
00:41:14,190 --> 00:41:15,670
born from the spiritual energy of heaven and earth?

914
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:18,200
Why should you be scared of the Five Eternals?

915
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:19,630
The Five Eternals are not scary.

916
00:41:19,630 --> 00:41:20,840
What's scary is the Contemplation Stone.

917
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,320
You have the Contemplation Stone in you,

918
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:24,620
so all the Eternals and demons in the world want you.

919
00:41:24,620 --> 00:41:26,030
Even if I'm a 1000-year-old tortoise,

920
00:41:26,030 --> 00:41:27,510
I wouldn't be able to handle it.

921
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:28,320
Alright.

922
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,280
Cut the crap.

923
00:41:29,620 --> 00:41:30,340
Either

924
00:41:30,370 --> 00:41:31,330
teach her,

925
00:41:31,350 --> 00:41:32,380
or

926
00:41:32,410 --> 00:41:34,010
give your life back to me now.

927
00:41:34,420 --> 00:41:36,020
Calm down. Calm down.

928
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:37,440
I'll teach her.

929
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:42,550
Are you sure you want this turtle who knows no bounds

930
00:41:42,550 --> 00:41:44,670
to be my master?

931
00:41:44,670 --> 00:41:46,470
What do you think he can teach me?

932
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:53,880
Eat this.

933
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:55,840
Your backlash will subside soon.

934
00:41:57,710 --> 00:41:58,810
Is it that powerful?

935
00:41:58,810 --> 00:42:00,040
Of course.

936
00:42:00,070 --> 00:42:03,800
If I rank second in healing,

937
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:07,120
no one dares to call themselves number one.

938
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:10,480
That's exactly what the quack who sold me fake medicine many years ago said.

939
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:13,110
How dare you compare me to those quacks?

940
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:14,880
Take it, or give it back to me.

941
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,400
I was just saying.

942
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:17,320
It's just I encountered too many swindlers

943
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:18,670
in the past.

944
00:42:18,800 --> 00:42:19,800
Of course I trust

945
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:21,800
the person Master introduced to me.

946
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:45,480
How is it?

947
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:47,080
Is the demonic pattern gone?

948
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:48,310
Look.

949
00:42:48,330 --> 00:42:49,350
Look.

950
00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:51,480
Old Turtle, look.

951
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,670
It's gone. It's gone.

952
00:42:52,670 --> 00:42:54,670
You're a girl. Watch your behavior.

953
00:42:55,360 --> 00:42:57,090
What's wrong with my behavior?

954
00:42:57,850 --> 00:42:58,920
Catch it.

955
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:01,070
What is it?

956
00:43:01,070 --> 00:43:02,670
Stay here with Old Turtle and learn from him.

957
00:43:02,670 --> 00:43:04,440
Contact me with this conch if anything happens.

958
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:05,880
I have to stay here alone?

959
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:08,110
What if the Eternal Race finds out?

960
00:43:08,110 --> 00:43:09,360
That's why I'm giving you this conch.

961
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:10,230
Take it with you wherever you go.

962
00:43:10,230 --> 00:43:11,150
Don't lose it

963
00:43:11,150 --> 00:43:12,000
or give it to others.

964
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,320
Otherwise, if you lose your life,

965
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:15,380
don't blame me for not reminding you.

966
00:43:17,160 --> 00:43:18,320
There's no need to warn me.

967
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:20,650
I'll teach her since you brought her here.

968
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:30,870
Let's start.

969
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:32,620
What do you mean start?

970
00:43:33,630 --> 00:43:35,890
Bow to me and take me as your master first.

971
00:43:35,990 --> 00:43:38,150
I, Bai Shuo, only bow to my parents, heaven and earth.

972
00:43:38,150 --> 00:43:40,230
I've never bowed to anyone else.

973
00:43:40,230 --> 00:43:41,360
If you want me to take you as my master,

974
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:43,590
you have to show me your real skills first.

975
00:43:43,590 --> 00:43:45,880
I won't teach you if you don't bow to me.

976
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:46,900
Really?

977
00:43:48,190 --> 00:43:49,880
Master.

978
00:43:50,710 --> 00:43:52,110
Go ahead.

979
00:43:52,110 --> 00:43:53,320
Your Highness.

980
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:55,150
I'll teach you.

981
00:43:55,150 --> 00:43:56,550
I surrender.

982
00:43:57,450 --> 00:43:58,780
Nothing.

983
00:43:58,800 --> 00:44:00,540
I just wanted to ask

984
00:44:03,550 --> 00:44:04,880
if you got home safely.

985
00:44:07,630 --> 00:44:09,510
I'll work hard and learn from Old Turtle.

986
00:44:09,510 --> 00:44:10,630
When I finish my studies,

987
00:44:10,630 --> 00:44:12,200
remember to come and pick me up.

988
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:12,880
Okay.

989
00:44:15,200 --> 00:44:16,280
Am I a good friend or not?

990
00:44:16,280 --> 00:44:17,410
I didn't tell on you.

991
00:44:20,110 --> 00:44:22,180
As the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle,

992
00:44:22,180 --> 00:44:24,240
you must have a lot of special skills.

993
00:44:24,580 --> 00:44:26,180
What will you teach me first?

994
00:44:30,450 --> 00:44:31,820
Watch

995
00:44:31,840 --> 00:44:32,880
carefully.

996
00:44:49,370 --> 00:44:50,730
Did you get it?

997
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:51,720
What?

998
00:44:52,230 --> 00:44:53,360
Breath holding.

999
00:44:53,730 --> 00:44:56,130
Are you sure this is a skill of the Eternals?

1000
00:44:57,760 --> 00:44:58,630
My disciple.

1001
00:44:58,880 --> 00:44:59,900
What's the most important thing

1002
00:44:59,900 --> 00:45:01,670
in a duel?

1003
00:45:01,720 --> 00:45:02,650
To defeat the enemy.

1004
00:45:02,650 --> 00:45:03,610
Wrong.

1005
00:45:03,640 --> 00:45:04,570
It's to survive.

1006
00:45:04,880 --> 00:45:08,070
What I taught you just now is my secret technique,

1007
00:45:08,100 --> 00:45:09,580
Turtle's Breath.

1008
00:45:09,630 --> 00:45:10,510
But of course,

1009
00:45:10,510 --> 00:45:12,400
you can also call it

1010
00:45:13,150 --> 00:45:14,360
Playing Dead.

1011
00:45:21,670 --> 00:45:22,760
I'll teach you something else.

